    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54 platform, featuring the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock. Mechanically, the VANOS system has been comprehensively overhauled, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly integrity. The rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to maintain chassis rigidity against high torque loads. The individual throttle bodies (ITBs) are perfectly synchronized, providing the razor-sharp throttle response characteristic of this 8,000 RPM naturally aspirated inline-six. All suspension components retain factory kinematics with fresh bushings, ensuring the precise handling profile the M-division intended. This is a turn-key, collector-grade specimen with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
