      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-quality vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior finish that is entirely free of rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections; the factory paint depth remains consistent across every panel. The interior is equally breathtaking, featuring supple leather with no bolster wear and that distinct 'new car' aroma. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the infotainment system, operates with factory-spec precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a lifetime of open-checkbook maintenance with a complete folder of service receipts included. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade specimen that drives as smoothly as the day it left the showroom floor.",
